headline: Super Micro Computer Rose More Than 300% to Start 2024. Can It Repeat That in 2025?
summary: First, let's take a look back at Supermicro's stock as it entered 2024.  There were a lot of signs pointing toward Supermicro having a ton of success because it makes components for computing servers as well as assembling full technology racks.  This business got a huge boost as artificial intelligence (AI) spending ramped up, and Supermicro was seen to benefit from a similar demand boost that powered Nvidia's (NASDAQ: NVDA) stock higher.
